<link rel="stylesheet" href="webbuild2.css" type="text/css"/>
d4 2
a5 2
<h2>WebBuild2<sup>1</sup></h2>
<h4>Front-end to build automation</h4>
d10 25
a34 32
  <li>
    <p>
<b>One-click builds</b>
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
Kick off a default-config suite of builds.
      </li><li>
Much like requesting a set of m-c nightlies; uses the api to do the defaults.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li><br />

  <li>
    <p>
<b>Advanced form</b>
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
Kick off special one-off builds.
      </li><li>
Kick off a suite with specific builds or platforms turned on or off.
      </li><li>
Change default behavior for this specific set of builds.
        <ul>
          <li>
Where to report to, what toolchain to use, etc.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
